title: Philippe Raschke
text: Philippe Raschke (born 19 September 1967, in <a href="Clermont-Ferrand">Clermont-Ferrand</a>) is a French former professional <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28football%29">defender</a>. While at Strasbourg he won the <a href="1995%20UEFA%20Intertoto%20Cup">1995 UEFA Intertoto Cup</a> and the <a href="Coupe%20de%20la%20Ligue">Coupe de la Ligue</a> in 1997. While at Sochaux he played as they won the <a href="2004%20Coupe%20de%20la%20Ligue%20Final">2004 Coupe de la Ligue Final</a>.
